DescriptionOfContractRequirement: THE PURPOSE OF MODIFICATION-05 TO CONTRACT W15P7T-06-D-A008/TASK ORDER 0051 IS AS FOLLOWS: 1. CLINS 0001 AND 0002 ARE HEREBY UNILATERALLY DEFINITIZED UNDER THIS TASK ORDER IN ACCORDANCE WITH DFARS 217.7404-3(B) AS A FIRM FIXED PRICE EFFORT IN THE AMOUNT OF $24,197,906.00. ALSO, THE PCO HAS UNILATERALLY DETERMINED THE MARS MUOS PHASE 3 EFFORT TO BE NON-COMMERCIAL UNDER CONTRACT MODIFICATION P00032, AND THIS TASK ORDER MODIFICATION 05, IN ACCORDANCE WITH FAR 15.403-1(C)(3)(I) AND THE TASK ORDER 0051 H0005 RE-OPENER PROVISION. A SEPARATE MODIFICATION TO CONTRACT W15P7T-06-D-A008 WILL BE FORTHCOMING TO ADD THE ASSOCIATED NON-COMMERCIAL FAR/DFARS CLAUSES. 2. AS A RESULT OF THIS UNILATERAL DEFINITIZATION, THE FUNDING SUMMARY IS HEREBY CHANGED FOR CLINS 0001 AND 0002 AS FOLLOWS: SLIN PREVIOUSLY FUNDED FUNDING THIS MOD TOTAL FUNDING 0001AA $ 7,271,143.00 - $2,054,795.00 $ 5,216,348.00 0002AA $10,334,403.80 $8,647,154.20 $18,981,558.00 3. UNDER THIS UNILATERAL PCO DEFINITIZATION OF CLIN 0001, THE PCO HAS DISALLOWED $921,891.00 IN TOTAL ACTUAL CONTRACTOR INCURRED COSTS AS FOLLOWS: SUBCONTRACTOR COSTS (-$878,601.00); AND MATERIAL COSTS (-$43,290.00). HOWEVER, THE CONTRACTOR CAN SUBMIT A REQUEST FOR EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT TO THE PCO IN ACCORDANCE WITH DFARS CLAUSE 252.243-7002 TO BE ADDED TO CONTRACT W15P7T-06-D-A008 UNDER THE FORTHCOMING MODIFICATION REFERENCED IN PARAGRAPH 1. ABOVE. 4. IF THE CONTRACTOR BELIEVES THAT THIS UNILATERAL PCO DEFINITIZATION OF CLIN 0002 INVOLVING CONVERSION OF THE MARS MUOS PHASE 3 TASK ORDER TO A NON-COMMERCIAL EFFORT REQUIRES AN ADJUSTMENT TO TASK ORDER 0051, THE CONTRACTOR HAS THIRTY (30) DAYS FROM THE DATE OF MODIFICATION 05 TO TASK ORDER 0051 TO SUBMIT A REVISED PROPOSAL. IT IS INCUMBENT UPON THE CONTRACTOR TO SUPPORT IN THEIR REVISED PROPOSAL SAID ADJUSTMENT WITH FULL DISCLOSURE OF ALL RELEVANT FACTS, AND IN ACCORDANCE WITH ALL APPLICABLE FEDERAL AND DEFENSE ACQUISITION REGULATIONS. THIS INCLUDES COMPLIANCE WITH FAR SUBPART 15.4 CONTRACT PRICING, TO INCLUDE SUBMISSION OF CERTIFIED COST AND PRICING DATA PURSUANT TO FAR 15.403-4(A)(1) AND 15.403-1(C)(3)(I), AND FAR 15.408, TABLE 15-2 -- INSTRUCTIONS FOR SUBMITTING COST/PRICE PROPOSALS WHEN CERTIFIED COST OR PRICING DATA ARE REQUIRED. 5. UNDER CLIN 002 MARS MUOS PHASE 3 TASK ORDER 0051 CONVERSION TO A NON-COMMERCIAL EFFORT, THE CONTRACTOR SHALL PROPOSE A FORM OF NON-COMMERICIAL CONTRACT FINANCING IN ACCORDANCE WITH FAR PART 32, AS PART OF ANY CONTRACTOR REVISED PROPOSAL SUBMISSION. IT SHOULD BE NOTED THAT ANY CONTRACTOR CHANGES OUTLINED IN A REVISED PROPOSAL SUBMISSION TO PREVIOUSLY PAID EVENT PAYMENT MILESTONES UNDER TASK ORDER 0051 MAY BE SUBJECT TO DCAA AUDIT. 6. THE GOVERNMENT SHALL OBTAIN DCAA AUDIT ASSISTANCE AS NECESSARY FOR RAYTHEON COST AND PROPOSAL SUBMISSIONS PROVIDED TO DATE FOR CLINS 0001 AND 0002. DCAA AUDIT ASSISTANCE MAY BE OBTAINED AS NECESSARY TO SUPPORT ANY CONTRACTOR REQUESTS FOR EQUITABLE ADJUSTMENT RESULTING FROM ADJUSTMENTS TO TASK ORDER 0051 AND FINAL DEFINITIZATION OF CLINS 0001 AND 0002.
